            The C-Mind name, logo, and the content of this website are the property of C-Mind LLC. Aspects of our technology are patent pending (U.S. App. No. 64/016,668). You may not reproduce or distribute site content without our written permission, except for personal, non-commercial reference.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900">No warranties</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            This website is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We do not guarantee that the site will be uninterrupted, error-free, or that its content is complete or current.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900">Limitation of liability</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            To the maximum extent permitted by law, C-Mind LLC will not be liable for any damages arising from your use of this website.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900">Contact</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Questions about these terms can be sent to <a href="mailto:info@c-mindcare.com" class="font-medium text-teal-700 hover:text-teal-800">info@c-mindcare.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
